list.abstract: community（[kəˈmjuːnəti]），英语单词，作名词用，为社区；社会；团体。短语搭配有community college（社区学院；社区中学），例句为“Keep the community safe from illnesses.（让社区远离疾病）”。 community名词类近义词有village、organization、body等。
《Community》（废柴联盟）是安东尼·罗素、乔·罗素等执导，切维·切斯、乔尔·麦克哈尔、伊薇特·尼科尔·布朗等主演的美国系列电视剧，第一季于2009年9月17日在美国首播。 该剧讲述的是回炉再造的律师杰夫·温格及其学习小组成员间的学习生活趣闻，在嬉笑怒骂之间道出了生活真谛的故事。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm Blair Wlorf, Chair of the community outreach committee.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是布莱尔·霍道夫，委员会社区分会的主席。

yingyinNormal.en: You thought the opposite of "stupid loser" was "community college graduate"?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得"很傻很衰"的反义词是"社区大学毕业生"？

yingyinNormal.en: This community here is called Angeline and we only have about 15 families, 20 families.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个社区叫安吉莉，只有大概十几二十户人家。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: He has major ties in the community, and he is as far from a flight risk as it's possible to be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对社区贡献良多而且他完全没有弃保潜逃的可能。

yingyinNormal.en: And I'm gonna Westwood Community College to be closer to him. He's my forever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要去上西木社区大学，那样就离他近些，他永远是我的唯一。

yingyinNormal.en: Walmart wanted to knock this down, build a store here. But the community put a stop to it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 沃尔玛想把这片拆光，建起超市，但是被社区阻止了。

yingyinNormal.en: Every year, our schools choose to support one local institution that we feel benefits our community.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每年，我们学校都会资助一所为我们社区造福的机构。

yingyinNormal.en: You have an average size home and an average community, and you decide to upgrade.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有个普通大小的房子，普通大小的社区，你决定住的再高级一点。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry, but are you asserting that the crack epidemic is exclusive to the black community?
yingyinNormal.zh: 打断一下，你是断定滥用大麻的问题，只在黑人社区中存在吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, men. Gather 'round. Teachable moment. Don't think of community service as a requirement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，各位，都过来，教学时间，不要把社区服务当成一种要求。

yingyinNormal.en: Before we lift a fork we lend a hand by going out in the community to serve some of our neighbors in need.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我们就餐前，我们会到社区中做义工为一些需要的邻居们服务。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me, I was in high school. Studying, keeping my nose clean, doing volunteer work for the community.
yingyinNormal.zh: 说什么呀，那时我才是高中生，就知道学习，洁身自爱，在社区做志愿服务。

yingyinNormal.en: But you got out. I got arrested. The judge said if I attended a community college, he'll seal my record.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你出来了。我被逮捕了，法官说如果我肯去上社区大学，他就封锁我的前科。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, there are a lot of successful people in this country who are community college graduates. Yeah, but you are neither.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很多成功人士都是从社区大学毕业的。没错，可你哪个都挨不上边。

yingyinNormal.en: Riles, I live in a Spanish-speaking community, I've heard it out my window all these years, so I've picked some up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小莱，我生活在说西语的社区这些话我都听了好几年了，所以就记住了一些。

yingyinNormal.en: Why do you have a history textbook? No. It's not a big deal. Just taking a class at the Pasadena Community College.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么会有一本历史课本啊？没什么啦，我就去了帕萨迪纳社区大学上课嘛。

yingyinNormal.en: But somehow, our little community, why, we came together, didn't we? We came together, didn't we? Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是不知怎地，我们这个小社区团结了起来，是不是？我们团结了起来，是不是？是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Whereas you, on the other hand, are a community college dropout who comes from the culture that wrote the book on tipping cows.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而你，只是社区大学辍学生，你们那的文化中，只有如何把牛推倒的书。

yingyinNormal.en: I've put a lot of thought into it. This community took a stand. If enough of them do, Congress won't have a choice but to act.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我考虑了很多。这个社区表明了它的立场。如果足够多的人站出来，国会只能行动。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me? I'm just wondering if you really gave it the old college try. Or in your case, the old community college try.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说什么？我只是在想，如果你能试试旧学院派的做法，或者就你而言，旧社区大学的做法。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
